### Prior Failure Patterns

Before starting work, check for known failure patterns from previous tasks:

```bash
harness search-failures --query "<relevant keywords>" --limit 10
```

Review results for recurring issues that may affect this task.  If prior patterns suggest known pitfalls, factor them into your approach.

